    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine vehicle that looks and feels as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, showing zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned with factory-tight tolerances. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any creases or wear, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a life of meticulous, open-checkbook maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. Included are all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a comprehensive folder of service records. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
